### 7. Lấy chi tiết văn bản
GET http://localhost:4000/api/documents/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Tải xuống file Word
GET http://localhost:4000/api/documents/1/download
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Xóa văn bản
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/documents/1
Content-Type: application/json

